Canadian Industry Minister Tony
Clement will comment at 1:45 p.m. on the proposed $3.2 billion
purchase of  TMX Group Inc . by  London Stock Exchange Group Plc ,
according to a statement e-mailed from his office today.  Clement has said the transaction may be subject to review
under foreign-investment legislation.  To contact the reporter on this story:
